## Building an APK Bundle
I want my game to run on Android for now, and for that, I will use [Cordova](https://cordova.apache.org/). First I need to install Cordova with `npm install -g cordova`, then [install Android Studio and yada yada](https://cordova.apache.org/docs/en/10.x/guide/platforms/android/index.html) and then finally create my project with `cordova create skate`.

Cordova will expect the build files to be in a `www/` folder, that's why I had to change my Webpack script before. Now I can simply run `cordova build --release android` and an unsigned APK file will be generated for me.

