With that in place, I need to create a trigger to hide/show that layer, and the best way to do it is when creating the map and the custom colliders, [which I explained in my devlog #3](/en/blog/games/third-game-devlog-of-skate-platformer/), and since I want to create the stages on `Tiled` and let the code figure out where these colliders need to be, I will create a loop that goes through all tiles to create colliders for the entire area of the layer, like the image below.

